column15: NoResetRequested is a dummy message doing nothing. It might be useful for integration in MQTT and HA automation. ErrorsAndFilter seems not working for me - but is specified.
Temporary settings which resets after few minutes
Does not reset after one minute with Sky300 with latest SW; this message is sent by Brink AirControl wall panel
